#group to plot
group_l=['CG', 'EG'] # ["CG", "EG"], ["CG"], ["EG"]
#protocol to plot
protocol='eo'
#sheets to plot
sheet_l=['gsr'] #['alpha']-one band or ['theta','alpha','SMR','beta']-multiple band
sheet_df_d={} #sheet df dict
#transform sheet columns 'epoch_a'
index_epoch_a=2 #choose an index of the list of lists
method="index_a_mean" # transform unicode to : "epoch_a_data", "index_a_data" or "index_a_mean"
scale=0.1 #scale the mean
for sheet in sheet_l:
    sheet_df_d[sheet] = pd.read_excel(database_path, sheet_name=sheet)
    sheet_df=sheet_df_d[sheet]
    #transform epoch_a
    for c in sheet_df.columns:
        if c.find('epoch_a')>-1:
            #print("TRANSFORMING: ",c)
            for r in sheet_df.index:
                cell_data=sheet_df.loc[r,c] #cell
                if not cell_data or not pd.notna(cell_data): continue #empty or nan value
                #print(sheet_df.loc[r,c])
                uni=cell_data#unicode cell
                cell_data=e2_f.convert_unicode(uni) #convert unicode cell
                if not cell_data: continue #dont substitute, its empty
                if method=="epoch_a_data":
                    sheet_df.loc[r,c]=cell_data
                index_a_data=[]#create index epoch data
                for epoch in cell_data:
                    index_a_data.append(epoch[index_epoch_a])
                cell_data=index_a_data
                if method=="index_a_data":
                    sheet_df.loc[r,c]=cell_data
                if method=="index_a_mean":
                    data=np.array(cell_data) # epoch array
                    data=data[np.logical_not(np.isnan(data))] #REMOVE NaN (EMPTY CELLS - OBLIGATORY)
                    data=data*scale#scale 
                    sheet_df.loc[r,c]=data.mean()
                #print(sheet_df.loc[r,c])
    
    #select subjects - using 'eeg_alpha_groups'
    select_subjects=False
    sufix='allsubjects'#default
    if select_subjects:
        sufix='NFT_+'
        group=protocol+'_'+sufix #group of subjects
        subjects_l=eeg_alpha_groups['subject'].loc[(eeg_alpha_groups[group]==1)].tolist() #select subjects to list
        sheet_df=sheet_df.loc[sheet_df['subject'].isin(subjects_l)] #get alpha features dataframe of subjects
    exclude_subjects=True
    if exclude_subjects:
        group=protocol+'_EX_SUB' #group of subjects
        subjects_l=eeg_alpha_groups['subject'].loc[(eeg_alpha_groups[group]==1)].tolist() #select subjects to list
        sheet_df=sheet_df.loc[sheet_df['subject'].isin(subjects_l) != True]    #print([alpha_df['subject'].isin(subjects_l) != True])
    sheet_df_d[sheet]=sheet_df #substitute sheet_df
#feature to plot
feat_l=['epoch_a'] #epoch_a was transformed to mean
#tasks to plot- [("x axis name","tasks to use")]
task_l=[]
if protocol=="eo":
    #task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_eo_2']), ("NFT_1",['alpha_eo_3']), ("NFT_2",['alpha_eo_5','alpha_eo_7']), ("NFT_3",['alpha_eo_9','alpha_eo_11']), ("NFT_4",['alpha_eo_14'])]
    task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_eo_2']), ("NFT_1",['alpha_eo_3']), ("PRIME_1", ["rest_eo_4", "breathingv6_eo_4","imageryv6_eo_4", "rest_eo_6", "breathingv6_eo_6","imageryv6_eo_6"]), ("NFT_2",['alpha_eo_5','alpha_eo_7']), ("PRIME_2", ["rest_eo_8", "breathingv6_eo_8","imageryv6_eo_8", "rest_eo_10", "breathingv6_eo_10","imageryv6_eo_10"]),("NFT_3",['alpha_eo_9','alpha_eo_11']), ("NFT_4",['alpha_eo_14'])]
if protocol=="ec":
    #task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_ec_1']), ("NFT_1",['alpha_ec_5','alpha_ec_7']), ("NFT_2",['alpha_eo_9','alpha_eo_11'])]
    task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_ec_1']), ("PRIME_1", ["rest_ec_4", "breathingv6_ec_4","imageryv6_ec_4", "rest_ec_6", "breathingv6_ec_6","imageryv6_ec_6"]), ("NFT_1",['alpha_ec_5','alpha_ec_7']),  ("PRIME_2", ["rest_ec_8", "breathingv6_ec_8","imageryv6_ec_8", "rest_ec_10", "breathingv6_ec_10","imageryv6_ec_10"]), ("NFT_2",['alpha_ec_9','alpha_ec_11'])]


#SAVE - file_sufix to add to filename and plot
file_sufix=protocol+'_'+feat_l[0]+'_'+sufix
save=False

#PLOT STATs
plot_stats=True
task_ref_stats=task_l[0][0]#reference task to make stats
#1) one-sample paired ttest: 1_measurement_var=tBAT, 1_nominal_var=subjects, 2_nominal_var=task_out-task_ref ; hipotheses: ; 
# biological question: Whether the measurment var has gone up or down between task_out and task_ref.
#null hypothesis: mean difference between paired observations is zero.
#2) two-sample ttest (independent or dependent samples): 1_measurement_var=tBAT, 1_nominal_var=Task=['Task_out' vs 'Task_ref'];
#assumption: normally distibuted; null hypothesis:  means of the measurement var are equal for the two categories.
#http://www.biostathandbook.com/pairedttest.html
stats_test='ttest_pair'#"ttest_pair"; 'ttest_ind' , 'ttest_rel'

stats_loc=-0.1
#PLOT BANDS
e2_f.plot_group(datadir, save=save,group_l=group_l,task_l=task_l, sheet_l=sheet_l, sheet_df_d=sheet_df_d, feat_l=feat_l, file_sufix=file_sufix, uplims=True, lolims=True, plot_stats=plot_stats, task_ref_stats=task_ref_stats,stats_test=stats_test, stats_loc=-0.1, scale=scale)

def plot_between_subjects(group_l=['CG', 'EG'], sheet_l=['alpha'], 
                          feat_l=['ratio_power_threshold'], 
                          protocol='eo', select_subjects=False, exclude_subjects=True,
                          save=False, plot_stats=True, stats_test='ttest_pair', 
                          scale=10, stats_loc=0.3, group_sufix='allsubjects'):
    #group to plot
    group_l=group_l # ["CG", "EG"], ["CG"], ["EG"]
    #protocol to plot
    protocol=protocol
    #sheets to plot
    sheet_l=sheet_l #['alpha']-one band or ['theta','alpha','SMR','beta']-multiple band
    sheet_df_d={} #sheet df dict
    for sheet in sheet_l:
        sheet_df_d[sheet] = pd.read_excel(database_path, sheet_name=sheet)
        #select subjects - using 'eeg_alpha_groups'
        sheet_df=sheet_df_d[sheet]
        select_subjects=select_subjects
        group_sufix=group_sufix#default
        if select_subjects and not group_sufix=='allsubjects':
            group_sufix=group_sufix
            group=protocol+'_'+group_sufix #group of subjects
            subjects_l=eeg_alpha_groups['subject'].loc[(eeg_alpha_groups[group]==1)].tolist() #select subjects to list
            sheet_df=sheet_df.loc[sheet_df['subject'].isin(subjects_l)] #get alpha features dataframe of subjects
        exclude_subjects=exclude_subjects
        if exclude_subjects:
            group=protocol+'_EX_SUB' #group of subjects
            subjects_l=eeg_alpha_groups['subject'].loc[(eeg_alpha_groups[group]==1)].tolist() #select subjects to list
            sheet_df=sheet_df.loc[sheet_df['subject'].isin(subjects_l) != True]    #print([alpha_df['subject'].isin(subjects_l) != True])
        sheet_df_d[sheet]=sheet_df #substitute sheet_df
    #feature to plot
    feat_l=feat_l #'ratio_power_threshold', 'tBAT', 'tonic_increase', 'tonic_increase_BAT'
    #tasks to plot- [("x axis name","tasks to use")]
    task_l=[]
    if protocol=="eo":
        #task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_eo_2']), ("NFT_1",['alpha_eo_3']), ("NFT_2",['alpha_eo_5','alpha_eo_7']), ("NFT_3",['alpha_eo_9','alpha_eo_11']), ("NFT_4",['alpha_eo_14'])]
        task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_eo_2']), ("NFT_1",['alpha_eo_3']), ("PRIME_1", ["rest_eo_4", "breathingv6_eo_4","imageryv6_eo_4", "rest_eo_6", "breathingv6_eo_6","imageryv6_eo_6"]), ("NFT_2",['alpha_eo_5','alpha_eo_7']), ("PRIME_2", ["rest_eo_8", "breathingv6_eo_8","imageryv6_eo_8", "rest_eo_10", "breathingv6_eo_10","imageryv6_eo_10"]),("NFT_3",['alpha_eo_9','alpha_eo_11']), ("NFT_4",['alpha_eo_14'])]
    if protocol=="ec":
        #task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_ec_1']), ("NFT_1",['alpha_ec_5','alpha_ec_7']), ("NFT_2",['alpha_eo_9','alpha_eo_11'])]
        task_l=[("BAS_0",['rest_ec_1']), ("PRIME_1", ["rest_ec_4", "breathingv6_ec_4","imageryv6_ec_4", "rest_ec_6", "breathingv6_ec_6","imageryv6_ec_6"]), ("NFT_1",['alpha_ec_5','alpha_ec_7']),  ("PRIME_2", ["rest_ec_8", "breathingv6_ec_8","imageryv6_ec_8", "rest_ec_10", "breathingv6_ec_10","imageryv6_ec_10"]), ("NFT_2",['alpha_ec_9','alpha_ec_11'])]


    #SAVE - file_sufix to add to filename and plot
    file_sufix=protocol+'_'+feat_l[0]+'_'+group_sufix
    save=save

    #PLOT STATs
    plot_stats=plot_stats
    task_ref_stats=task_l[0][0]#reference task to make stats
    #1) one-sample paired ttest: 1_measurement_var=tBAT, 1_nominal_var=subjects, 2_nominal_var=task_out-task_ref ; hipotheses: ; 
    # biological question: Whether the measurment var has gone up or down between task_out and task_ref.
    #null hypothesis: mean difference between paired observations is zero.
    #2) two-sample ttest (independent or dependent samples): 1_measurement_var=tBAT, 1_nominal_var=Task=['Task_out' vs 'Task_ref'];
    #assumption: normally distibuted; null hypothesis:  means of the measurement var are equal for the two categories.
    #http://www.biostathandbook.com/pairedttest.html
    stats_test=stats_test#"ttest_pair"; 'ttest_ind' , 'ttest_rel'
    scale=scale
    stats_loc=stats_loc#localization of stats
    e2_f.plot_group(datadir, save=save,group_l=group_l,task_l=task_l, sheet_l=sheet_l, sheet_df_d=sheet_df_d, feat_l=feat_l, file_sufix=file_sufix, uplims=True, lolims=True, plot_stats=plot_stats, task_ref_stats=task_ref_stats,stats_test=stats_test,stats_loc=stats_loc, scale=scale)
